{"tid":1100053,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【男子睡夢中遭室友以人臉識別盜走逾萬元】","createTime":"2019-04-10T07:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T12:13:33.000Z","uid":1251,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b4ac7fed753b0138bafde384a07c7e394f67b1","tid":1100053,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:35:19.000Z","msg":"咩機黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />合埋眼都用到face id?<br />\n<br />\n【男子睡夢中遭室友以人臉識別盜走逾萬元】<br />\n<br />\n住在浙江寧波市一間宿舍的袁先生，醒來後發現銀行卡內少了一萬多元。警方調查發現，疑犯是和袁先生同住的兩名男子，他們趁袁先生熟睡，偷偷把他的手機靠近臉部解鎖開機，再從袁先生微信綁定的銀行卡，轉走一萬多元。<br />\n<br />\n#人臉識別<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2085805074897301?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2085805074897301%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=d4590068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2085805074897301?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"59ce92ccb87f8a993939b6a99e630656a2d54095","tid":1100053,"uid":109383,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"關face id咩事？<br />\n<br />\n睇個下巴位粗過邊框就知唔係iPhone啦"},{"pid":"ad2e6bffbe1959bbdd8dea55c1c233d5dcc510d3","tid":1100053,"uid":204398,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"An機唔係叫Face ID<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得個2D就算啦"},{"pid":"d781833d20657a0b0c1e565b0a550bfa8a0c59ec","tid":1100053,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"59ce92ccb87f8a993939b6a99e630656a2d54095","tid":1100053,"uid":109383,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"關face id咩事？<br />\n<br />\n睇個下巴位粗過邊框就知唔係iPhone啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:52:59.000Z","msg":"所以我咪問咩機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1